 were farmers but under jacques’ vision they ultimately started making their own wines in the auspiciously spectacular  vintage we’ve been drinking dieboltvallois blanc de blancs as our “anytime” champagne for years so we’re just pleased that we’ve found more to offer to our clients and that so many people seem to agree with our assessment of this sparkler’s stellar quality and value tasting notes nv dieboltvallois blanc de blancs brut wine access the dieboltvallois blanc de blancs is pale goldgreen in hue tiny bubbles of great persistence precise nose of citrus orange pith ripe green apple and freshly baked brioche taut tightly wound and complex on the attack with a chalkinfused core of apple pear and ripe lemon finishing with terrific tension and vibrancy  points wine  spirits the texture is supple the flavors succulent and appetite inducing  points wine spectator this is fresh and floral on the nose with a chalky mousse and cleancut acidity framing flavors of poached pear and white cherry fruit clover honey and slivered almond on the palate lasting zesty finish of grated ginger and ground spice drink now through  wine facts type sparkling varietal chardonnay country france region champagne alcohol by volume     bottles   bottles   bottles by law this offer may only be shipped to the following states ak az ca co ct dc fl ga hi ia id il in ks la ma me mn mo mt nc nd ne nh nm nv oh or pa sc tn tx va vt wa wi wv wy shipping included offer does not apply to shipments to hawaii and alaska the world’s finest wines direct from the source we curate exclusive wines from every region cutting out the middlemen to bring you the best prices simple enough get access great wine is made with extraordinary optimism and grapes winemaking like anything else worth doing requires you trust your instincts and take some risks we take the risk out of finding extraordinary wines but none of the adventure shop our wines featured in the store extraordinary vintages handselected by our exper